lead_paragraph: Shown here is the look that defined 2015: ankle boots, a long stretch of leg, a flowerlike blossom top and a fur pompom at the peak of knitted hats.

abstract: Bill Cunningham shares photos of stylish New Yorkers wearing 2015 trends during New York Fashion Week.
